First Department,

September, 1982

(September 3, 1982) In the Matter of Diosdado Rivera et al., Appellants, v Gilberto G. Valentin, Respondent.

Judgment, Supreme Court, Bronx County, entered on September 1, 1982, unanimously affirmed, without costs and without disbursements. No opinion. Concur — Kupferman, J. P., Lupiano, Silverman, Bloom and Fein, JJ.
